A '''spice tanker''' was a craft used to transport [[Spice/Legends|spice]] along trade routes. [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] and [[Princess/Legends|Princess]] [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]] used one to secretly transport medical supplies for the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] but were intercepted by an [[Imperial-class Star Destroyer/Legends|Imperial Star Destroyer]]. As they tried to make the jump to [[Hyperspace/Legends|hyperspace]], the ship was damaged, and the craft traveled beyond [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]] into the [[Intergalactic Void|intergalactic void]], where they encountered the living spacecraft known as [[Ship (sentient spacecraft)|Ship]]. Ship eventually repaired their tanker and returned the pair back to their home galaxy to continue their mission.

Spice tankers had been used for millennia by the ruling authorities of [[Kessel/Legends|Kessel]] to transport [[Glitterstim/Legends|glitterstim]] to all parts of the galaxy.

